description: a(1) = 1, a(A206074(n)) = A014580(a(n)), a(A205783(1+n)) = A091242(a(n)), where A014580 [respectively A091242] give binary codes for irreducible [resp. reducible] polynomials over GF(2), while A206074 and A205783 give similar codes for polynomials with coefficients 0 or 1 that are irreducible [resp. reducible] over Q.
